MultilineDescription.SourceString: Level 1 : Increases Sword damage based on Ninja Lair Rating.
MultilineDescription.LocalizedString: Level 1 : Increases Sword damage based on Ninja Lair Rating.

MultilineDescription.SourceString: Level 2 : Reduces the Energy cost of Sword special attacks by 50%.
MultilineDescription.LocalizedString: Level 2 : Reduces the Energy cost of Sword special attacks by 50%.

MultilineDescription.SourceString: Level 3 : Increases the Durability of Swords based on Ninja Lair Rating.
MultilineDescription.LocalizedString: Level 3 : Increases the Durability of Swords based on Ninja Lair Rating.

MultilineDescription.SourceString: Level 4 : Reduces the Energy cost of Sword special attacks by 100%.
MultilineDescription.LocalizedString: Level 4 : Reduces the Energy cost of Sword special attacks by 100%.

MultilineDescription.SourceString: Level 5 : Poison Blade : Sword Critical Hits cause the target to become Afflicted with poison, dealing damage over time.
MultilineDescription.LocalizedString: Level 5 : Poison Blade : Sword Critical Hits cause the target to become Afflicted with poison, dealing damage over time.
